{
  "texts": [
    "First, the Yolo v8-l and Yolo v8-s excel in performance with high mean average precision (mAP), mAP 50, and mAP 75.",
    "This indicates that these two models have satisfied foreign object detection capabilities for high-precision application scenarios.",
    "In addition, the Yolo v8-s strikes a balance between speed and precision and may be an attractive choice for real-world applications.",
    "However, there also exist lower performance models, such as Yolo v7-l and Yolo v7-tiny, which perform poorly in detecting foreign objects.",
    "Similarly, SSD and RetinaNet (ResNet18) have relatively low performance."
  ]
}